{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Chandler Moisen","author":"Chandler Moisen"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2b8f6941-fb4a-5773-9daf-f97994316076","excerpt":"For a new side project, Keming, my partner and I needed to quickly validate interest in our product. To do so, we designed and built simple landing page scoped…","html":"<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/834a2bc4e4814d60a2e7ef3aaa79b7b5/71a9e/airtable-logo.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 43.23094425483504%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"airtable logo\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/834a2bc4e4814d60a2e7ef3aaa79b7b5/b9e4f/airtable-logo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/834a2bc4e4814d60a2e7ef3aaa79b7b5/cf440/airtable-logo.png 148w,\n/static/834a2bc4e4814d60a2e7ef3aaa79b7b5/d2d38/airtable-logo.png 295w,\n/static/834a2bc4e4814d60a2e7ef3aaa79b7b5/b9e4f/airtable-logo.png 590w,\n/static/834a2bc4e4814d60a2e7ef3aaa79b7b5/71a9e/airtable-logo.png 879w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>For a new side project, <a href=\"https://keming.io\">Keming</a>, my partner and I needed to quickly validate interest in our product. To do so, we designed and built simple landing page scoped to the following constraints:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Allow users to submit interest and personal data</li>\n<li>Store this data safely, in an easily accessible format</li>\n<li>Retain control over all styling / branding </li>\n<li>No server-side code</li>\n<li>Completely static and easily deployable through <a href=\"https://www.netlify.com/\">Netlify</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>As we are bootstrapping Keming, we did not have an immediate requirement for a fully-fledged backend - even a simple <a href=\"https://github.com/pallets/flask\">Flask</a> application felt like overkill.</p>\n<p>At the same time, we did not want to release with a <a href=\"https://www.google.com/forms/about/\">Google Form</a> as we hypothesized the market we are targeting would be put off by something so crude.</p>\n<!-- 1. A new side project requiring collection of names and email addresses\n2. No need for firebase or any serious backend\n3. Validating the idea\n4. Initially reached for google sheets as I consume this product daily\n5. Usually a fan of google’s API’s and documentation - but there was a bit too much effort with google sheets API\n6. Recalled air table from work at GA\n7. Up and running in minutes - incredible developer experience\n8. Here’s how I did it: -->","frontmatter":{"title":"Airtable: Bootstrapping Made Easy","date":"December 21, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/airtable/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/you-can-filter-like-that/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"You Can Filter Like That?"}},"next":null}}